<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Services | Trusted Household &amp; Childcare</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <section class="page-hero">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Tailored staffing solutions for every household need.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="services-preview">
        <h2 class="section-title">Explore Dedicated Dubai Services</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Learn more about our private introduction process for the most requested childcare and household roles.</p>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#128118;</div>
                <h3>Nanny in Dubai</h3>
                <p>Private nanny introductions for families seeking trusted full-time, live-in, live-out, or travel-aware childcare support.</p>
                <a href="/nanny-in-dubai" class="card-link">View Nanny Service &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#128155;</div>
                <h3>Babysitter in Dubai</h3>
                <p>Flexible evening, weekend, occasional, and short-term babysitting support through a discreet consultation-led process.</p>
                <a href="/babysitter-in-dubai" class="card-link">View Babysitter Service &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">&#127968;</div>
                <h3>Housekeeper in Dubai</h3>
                <p>Experienced housekeeping introductions for refined home care, laundry, wardrobe support, and daily organization.</p>
                <a href="/housekeeper-in-dubai" class="card-link">View Housekeeper Service &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-detail">
        <div class="service-block">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Professional Nannies</h2>
                <p>Our nannies are experienced childcare professionals, fluent in English and trained in early childhood development. Each candidate holds certifications in first aid and child safety.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Full-time, live-in, or live-out arrangements</li>
                    <li>Newborn care specialists available</li>
                    <li>Educational activity planning</li>
                    <li>Multi-child household experience</li>
                    <li>Travel nanny services</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-block">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Private Chefs</h2>
                <p>From daily family meals to formal entertaining, our chefs bring international culinary expertise to your kitchen. Specializing in Asian, Mediterranean, and fusion cuisines.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Daily meal preparation and planning</li>
                    <li>Dietary restriction management</li>
                    <li>Event and dinner party catering</li>
                    <li>Kitchen inventory and procurement</li>
                    <li>Menu development and nutrition consulting</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-block">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Executive Housekeepers</h2>
                <p>Our housekeepers maintain your home to 5-star hospitality standards. Trained in luxury property management and household organization.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Deep cleaning and daily maintenance</li>
                    <li>Laundry and wardrobe management</li>
                    <li>Household inventory and supply management</li>
                    <li>Vendor coordination</li>
                    <li>Event preparation and hosting support</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service-block highlight">
            <div class="service-info">
                <h2>Careful Selection &amp; Consultation</h2>
                <p>We focus on trust, quality, and discretion. Every candidate is personally reviewed through a structured selection process before we make an introduction.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Screened, vetted, and personally reviewed candidates</li>
                    <li>Reference checks where available</li>
                    <li>Structured, multi-stage selection process</li>
                    <li>We can discuss family requirements, candidate suitability, and local process considerations during consultation</li>
                    <li>Serving international families worldwide, with priority coverage across Armenia, Georgia, Hong Kong, Japan, Singapore, the UAE, and Saudi Arabia</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Need a Custom Staffing Solution?</h2>
        <p>Contact us to discuss your specific requirements.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">Get in Touch</a>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
